                         <!--
TurboCheckout maintains an exclusion list of elements containing checkboxes (https://tiny.amazon.com/10fqaob7u/codeamazpackTurbblobfcfasrc).
When any of these checkbox is marked as selected, turbo checkout is suppressed and customer goes through regular SPC flow.
Element below will be added to exclusion list mentioned above, and payment-options-checkbox will be marked as selected
when UFO offer is selected to ensure turbo checkout experience is suppressed anf customer goes through regular SPC flow
on clicking buy now.
-->
<div id="payment-options-feature" class="a-section aok-hidden"><input type="checkbox" class="payment-options-checkbox aok-hidden"/>
