== --><button k-on-click="isLongPress_onP_123_54" k-on-mousedown="isLongPress_onP_125_5" k-on-mouseup="onPressOut_onLo_126_5" aria-label="閉じる" data-testid="close-button" style="border: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-align: inherit; font: inherit; border-radius: 0; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWz_S8Xm" k-observe k-use="7ebccb91-564a-4d0c-92ac-2a20d028b399" k-aria-checked="tmpCoalesce_tmp_138_54" k-aria-pressed="tmpCoalesce_tmp_139_54" k-aria-selected="tmpCoalesce_tmp_140_55" k-aria-disabled="tmpCoalesce_tmp_141_55" k-style="inlineStyles_146_3" k-class="mergedStyles_147_3" onclick><img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/sash/FQQMS6xydSSApTa.png" k-metric-loaded-enabled="false" aria-hidden="true" style="display:inline-block;height:12px;width:12px;object-fit:cover;" class="aui-primitive __HcWIi-bS7X-z"/></button><!-- k-injected k-component-close --><!-- k-injected k-component-close --></div><span style="white-space: pre-line;" data-testid="aspect-summary" class="aui-primitive __P0nNOOvpt01x __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">お客様はこのロマサガ2のリメイクについて高く評価しています。良作リメイクで、グラフィックや演出が秀逸だと感じています。また、フルリメイクのため新しいゲーム感覚で楽しめると好評です。BGMも最高で、時間を忘れてプレイできるほど素晴らしい作品だと述べています。</span><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z __P0nNOOKHIwIJ"><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWNvbXBvbmVudCI6IlNuaXBwZXRMaXN0LXA3WW9hU2tvbnBtRVNMViIsImstaWQiOiIxZTk5MjNlYi1iNzJmLTQ5ZTktYmI2YS05NTI2NjQ5ODdlZTIiLCJrLWNvbXBvc2VkIjoiU25pcHBldExpc3RfYXNwXzEwMF8yNSIsImstcGFyZW50IjoiOGEwZjQ5N2MtODhmNi00MjkwLThjYjMtNGNmYzgwNmM4YTkyIiwiay1kYXRhIjp7fX0= --><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z"><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z __P0nNOOvpt01x"><div data-csa-c-type="uxElement" data-csa-c-item-id="cr-product-insights-detail-page_read-more-link" data-csa-c-pos="" data-csa-c-posx="" data-csa-c-posy="" data-cs