OnsidmFsdWUiOiJkaXYifX0= --><div id="rh_controls_aspect_5" role="tabpanel" data-testid="bottomsheet-content-ストーリー" style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uFAv __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z" k-observe k-use="f62206fe-854a-470f-a204-40bbbc0519f2" k-style="inlineStyles_235_5" k-class="mergedStyles_236_5" onclick><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z"><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IY0d __P0nNOOvpt01x __HcWluv-7J"><div data-testid="mentions-inline" style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IY0d"><span style="white-space: pre-line;" class="aui-primitive __HcWWkUdHN __HcWNg-FAv __3LVrZoFAv">26人のお客様がストーリーに言及し、23人が肯定的、3人が否定的です</span><span style="white-space: pre-line;" aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ"><span style="white-space: pre-line;" class="aui-primitive"><span style="white-space: pre-line;" class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">26人のお客様が「ストーリー」に言及しています</span></span></span><span style="white-space: pre-line;" aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __dChWb2ruQw4B __P0nNOOzO001x __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">23肯定的</span><span style="white-space: pre-line;" aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __dChF3jO2MCfBw4B __P0nNOOzO001x __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">3否定的</span></div><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWV4cGFuZCI6Il84Ml8yOSIsImstaWQiOiI2YTZjYmFhYy1hY2IxLTRiNWQtOThkNS03OTUxOTUxODI4M2EiLCJrLXBhcmVudCI6IjFhMWI3N2MwLTZiMTctNDQ4OS1iYzk1LTQ0Yjk4ZDcwY2QyZSJ9 --><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWV4cGFuZC1sZXQiOiJhY2Nlc3NpYmlsaXR5U3RfMTE2XzExIiwiay1wYXJlbnQiOiJlMGJlYjU2MS04N2JlLTQ5YTYtYTNmMy02MjI4YzZhZjIzZjciLCJrLWRhdGEiOnt9fQ== --><button k-on-click="isLongPress_onP_123_54" k-on-mousedown="isLongPress_onP_125_5" k-on-mouseup="onPressOut_onLo_126_5" aria-label="閉じる" data-testid="close-button" style="border: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-align: inherit; font: inherit; border-radius: 0; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWz_S8Xm" k-observe k-use="e0beb561-87be-49a6-a3f3-6228c6af23f7" k-aria-checked="tmpCoalesce_tmp_138_54" k-aria-pressed="tmpCoalesce_tmp_139_54" k-aria-selected="tmpCoalesce_tmp_140_55" k-aria-disabled="tmpCoalesce_tmp_141_55" k-style="inlineStyles_146_3" k-class="mergedStyles_147_3" onclick><img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/sash/FQQMS6xydSSApTa.png" k-metric-loaded-enabled="false" aria-hidden="true" style="display:inline-block;height:12px;width:12px;object-fit:cover;" class="aui-primitive __HcWIi-bS7X-z"/></button><!-- k-injected k-component-close --><!-- k-injected k-component-close --></div><span style="white-space: pre-line;" data-testid="aspect-summary" class="aui-primitive __P0nNOOvpt01x __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">お客様はこのゲームについて、ストーリーが良く、ドラマ性がアップしたと評価しています。エンディング後の後日譚シーンが特に良いと感じており、キャットが振り向くシーンで涙腺がやられるという声もあります。また、ボス戦の迫力を出すシーンもカッコ良いと好評です。一方で、全体的に薄味でツッコミ所が多いという指摘もあります。</span><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z __P0nNOOKHIwIJ"><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWNvbXBvbmVudCI6IlNuaXBwZXRMaXN0LXA3WW9hU2tvbnBtRVNMViIsImstaWQiOiI0NGQ2MjQyYS04ZGE2LTQ2OTgtOTQ0NS02NTFkMjEzYWRlYzciLCJrLWNvbXBvc2VkIjoiU25pcHBldExpc3RfYXNwXzEwMF8yNSIsImstcGFyZW50IjoiMWExYjc3YzAtNmIxNy00NDg5LWJjOTUtNDRiOThkNzBjZDJlIiwiay1kYXRhIjp7fX0= --><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z"><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z __P0nNOOvpt01x"><div data-csa-c-type="uxElement" data-csa-c-item-id="cr-product-insights-detail-page_read-more-link" data-csa-c-pos="" data-csa-c-posx="" data-csa-c-posy="" data-csa-c-owner="CustomerReviews" data-csa-c-item-type="" data-csa-c-parent-element-id="" class="aui-primitive" data-csa-c-slot-id="cr-product-insights-detail-page_read-more-link"><span style="white-space: pre-line;" class="aui-primitive _