e __SAR2l0zNyyuZ __SARCET4AB">不満なのがジャンプの採用</span><span style="white-space: pre-line;" class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">。原作でもダッシュ時は跳んでましたが、結局、何に使うかといえば宝箱を取りにくくするだけ。他のギミックもなく、ストレスになるだけ。 後はSwitch版のロードの長さ。...</span></span><span style="white-space: pre-line;" aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">&quot;</span><span style="white-space: pre-line;" aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive"> </span><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWNvbXBvbmVudCI6IlRleHRMaW5rLXZHcGhSM0FHbzlwX0pHWiIsImstaWQiOiI2ZGRmNDJmYS02ZGJhLTQxODgtODI0MC1lYjMxNGFmMDMwODAiLCJrLWRhdGEiOnt9fQ== --><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWV4cGFuZC1sZXQiOiJ0YXJnZXRTdHJfNTZfNSIsImstcGFyZW50IjoiY2NlYzA1ZmMtZTYxYi00MDMwLTllMjEtMWU1NWViMGY2Yzg5Iiwiay1kYXRhIjp7InZhbHVlIjoiX3RvcCJ9fQ== --><!-- k-injected k+b64  --><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWV4cGFuZC1sZXQiOiJocmVmU3RyXzgxXzUiLCJrLXBhcmVudCI6ImNjZWMwNWZjLWU2MWItNDAzMC05ZTIxLTFlNTVlYjBmNmM4OSIsImstZGF0YSI6eyJ2YWx1ZSI6Ii9ncC9jdXN0b21lci1yZXZpZXdzL1IzRTJSM1dRMTU5UUU2In19 --><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWV4cGFuZC1sZXQiOiJ1c2VIcmVmXzgyXzUiLCJrLXBhcmVudCI6ImNjZWMwNWZjLWU2MWItNDAzMC05ZTIxLTFlNTVlYjBmNmM4OSIsImstZGF0YSI6eyJ2YWx1ZSI6dHJ1ZX19 --><a href="/gp/customer-reviews/R3E2R3WQ159QE6" target="_top" tabindex="0" data-testid="read-more" k-on-mousedown="pressed_onMouse_105_5" k-on-mouseup="pressed_onMouse_106_5" k-on-mouseenter="onMouseIn_107_32" k-on-mouseleave="onMouseOut_108_33" class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ __SAR2l0N01yuZ" k-observe k-use="ccec05fc-e61b-4030-9e21-1e55eb0f6c89" k-class="mergedStyles_113_3" onclick><!-- k-injected k+b64 eyJrLW9ic2VydmUiOiIiLCJrLWNvbXBvbmVudCI6IlRleHQtSENPUU52M001MW9lY0tfIiwiay1pZCI6ImI0MzQyM2Q0LTA2M2QtNDBmNS1hYTYwLTNlNWI2NzAyOTFjYSIsImstY29tcG9zZWQiOiJUZXh0X3N0YXRlZnVsU3RfMTE0XzUiLCJrLXBhcmVudCI6ImNjZWMwNWZjLWU2MWItNDAzMC05ZTIxLTFlNTVlYjBmNmM4OSIsImstZGF0YSI6e319 --><span style=